name: Inner Child
description: *Sound ON* A reminder to take that leap! Don't let fear hold you back and don't take life too seriously. Tune into your inner child. Play, smile, love, explore, create, laugh, use your imagination, be a kid! Lighten up & Be free! Life's too short to be a constant adult. This piece encompasses many memorable aspects of my childhood and also has some hidden voices and meaningful objects that aren't so obvious at first glance.
